<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>Request to Add a New Car Brand</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    .message-container {
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
    }
    .message-title {
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .message-content {
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .signature {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-style: italic;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="message-container">
  <div class="message-title">Request to Add a New Car Brand</div>
  <div class="message-content">
    <p>Dear Manager,</p>
    <p>I would like to express a request to add a new car brand to your inventory.</p>
    <p>Information about the new car brand:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Name:</strong> {{this.brand}}</li>
    </ul>
    <p>I would appreciate your attention to this request. Please inform me about the next steps.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="signature">
    <p>Best regards,</p>Q
    <p>{{this.userId}}</p>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
